.TH "runJS" "1" "" "SequoiaDB User Manuals" ""
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
runJS \- Execute the JavaScript code remotely.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]\f[I]runJS( <code> )\f[]\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
Cmd
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Execute the JavaScript code remotely.
.PP
\f[B]Note:\f[]
.PP
	runJS() should be called by remote cmd obj
.RE
.SH PARAMETERS
.PP
.TS
tab(@);
l l l l l l.
T{
0
T}@T{
Name
T}@T{
Type
T}@T{
Default
T}@T{
Description
T}@T{
Required or not
T}
_
